      <extensionElements>
         <signavio:signavioDiagramMetaData metaKey="meta-processdescription" metaValue="After the approval of the general ledger (GL) maintenance request, accounts can be added to the GL. This requires an update of the appropriate account file/table.  Accounts may also be added to sub-ledgers (A/P, A/R, assets, banks, etc.).  Once created, these accounts must be assigned to account groups."/>
